		(uuid "fcc29e63-26c3-4154-b070-949dcae2d850")
	)
	(text "24-30V input, AMS1117-3.3 + AMS1117-5.0, bulk caps 100uF, decoupling 100nF per LDO.\nFrom KXKM BMU v2 power.kicad_sch.\nInput range: 24V-30V (battery pack nominal).\nOutput 1: 3.3V @ 800mA max (AMS1117-3.3).\nOutput 2: 5.0V @ 800mA max (AMS1117-5.0).\nThermal pad required for both LDOs at full load.\nAdd input TVS diode (SMAJ33A) for transient protection."
		(at 76.2 38.1 0)
